{"tid":1573304,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"新加密forum拋磚","createTime":"2019-09-16T03:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T09:59:15.000Z","uid":96402,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"560f6313edc9209a048b680970a74238f957ffdf","tid":1573304,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:06:15.000Z","msg":"想拋下磚睇下你地點諗<br />\n由於其實連登已經正式被入侵<br />\nP牌作用大不大見仁見智<br />\n有啲user帶風向都好難判斷<br />\n因為其實全部嘢都係public<br />\n問題係如果連登最後被ban<br />\n我地應該點傳遞資訊<br />\n我見之前都有唔少巴打整過其他討論區<br />\n咁我諗緊如果我地開個新嘅討論區<br />\n主要目的係可以secure到所有info<br />\n防止假消息/壞風向/狗臥底入侵傳播<br />\n<br />\n條件：<br />\n<br />\n1.只有參與/參與過遊行嘅人先可以加入<br />\n2.用invite呢種形式register 同時需要isp email<br />\n3.一個user limit佢只可以invite例如max兩個人（如果擔心普及性 其實pass down 廿幾次就可以普及到二百萬人 可以自己計下條式）<br />\n4.如果leak咗都容易trace到個root 因為有個「user hierarchy」喺度 睇返個connection. <br />\n5.可以繼續加入加密/唔加密function. reveal<br />\nselective info比非user<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.如果冇鬼嘅話 可以確保到資料嘅真實性<br />\n2.因為親密關係性質嘅invitation可以令有鬼嘅機會細好多<br />\n3.容易追究邊個係鬼<br />\n4.追究上黎 鬼invite嘅branch可以全部remove<br />\n5.所有嘢大前提係你respect個rule invite你真係信得過嘅人<br />\n6.會比連登嚴肅好多 business啲 唔會係troll<br />\n7.保障私隱<br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n1.未諗到server點維繫（因為非牟利性質）<br />\n<br />\n大家討論下有咩改善<br />\n同埋覺得可唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853cb77eb690d3feb14a01c4db57488edf430410","tid":1573304,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:11:24.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dfa399ba59e84b24aa2581670c7ebf2089f3a0c","tid":1573304,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:49:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"784436e05f0c8ba4383710272f3ee355b6f2f979","tid":1573304,"uid":2189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0547ce4c03e0fa270b141c32a34ae08e41aca7a","tid":1573304,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"784436e05f0c8ba4383710272f3ee355b6f2f979","tid":1573304,"uid":2189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:32:39.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講清楚小小<br />\n但嗰二千要自己搵係慢好多<br />\n我建議係自己pass down比最親密嗰兩個<br />\n嗰兩個再pass比自己最親密嗰兩個<br />\n咁樣好似安全好多"},{"pid":"2787530636de1436f8246ea1261ea217cdde9326","tid":1573304,"uid":289686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:38:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06c7e1cb6609dbeb25a483c5efde105d3553f43a","tid":1573304,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2787530636de1436f8246ea1261ea217cdde9326","tid":1573304,"uid":289686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:38:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"宜家用invite黎register<br />\n容易好多搵到鬼嗰個branch<br />\n咁就可以一下freeze晒啲鬼"},{"pid":"fbd991ec4959abc91af4b3230397cd98bcd7cf6a","tid":1573304,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"毒撚邊緣人搵唔到人驗證<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e025126eded26286bb94762e1b2bea9198e9066f","tid":1573304,"uid":56610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:00:22.000Z","msg":"可行 支持"},{"pid":"a5eb7d70522b8e8cdf04f5c318f674179a5bbf3a","tid":1573304,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0547ce4c03e0fa270b141c32a34ae08e41aca7a","tid":1573304,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"784436e05f0c8ba4383710272f3ee355b6f2f979","tid":1573304,"uid":2189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:32:39.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講清楚小小<br />\n但嗰二千要自己搵係慢好多<